graph TB
    subgraph "Frontend (React)"
        App[App Root]
        Home[Home Page]
        Workspace[Workspace Page]

        App --> Home
        App --> Workspace

        Home --> ProjectForm[Project Form]
        Home --> ProjectList[Project List]

        Workspace --> CodeEditor[Code Editor]
        Workspace --> LogViewer[Log Viewer]
        Workspace --> StatusBoard[Status Board]
        Workspace --> DecisionTrace[Decision Trace Panel]

        StatusBoard --> AgentCard[Agent Status Cards]
        LogViewer --> WSClient[WebSocket Client]
    end

    API[Backend API] -.->|WebSocket| WSClient
    API -.->|REST| ProjectForm
    API -.->|REST| ProjectList